      <title>create a small bottle cylinder box</title>
      <link>/blog/posts/create_a_small_bottle_cylinder_box/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Feb 2022 08:23:00 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>/blog/posts/create_a_small_bottle_cylinder_box/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://konubinix.eu/braindump/posts/tag_learning_3d_printing/?title=tag_learning_3d_printing#&#34;&gt;tag: learning 3D printing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;first-attempt-the-square-one&#34;&gt;first attempt: the square one&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is the fastest model I made. It&amp;rsquo;s just two squares with a boolean operation.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;/blog/ipfs/bafybeickotxpnjv4qye2fbkk5e7q4edk563tpxjca7svcxgj2nbom4c7oa/stl_viewer.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;stl_cont&#34; id=&#34;stl_cont_dc6c192a1e2d8d90daa1990178ce2147&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;script&gt;var stl_viewer=new StlViewer(document.getElementById(&#34;stl_cont_dc6c192a1e2d8d90daa1990178ce2147&#34;), { models: [ {id:0, filename:&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafkreifcdhvvkfgzzpyg2h5tyarwhrmeyshwkobccawt4ets2uiy3z2o2i?filename=square_box.stl&#34;} ] });&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;(&lt;a href=&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafkreifcdhvvkfgzzpyg2h5tyarwhrmeyshwkobccawt4ets2uiy3z2o2i?filename=square_box.stl&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-download&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;then-the-cylinder&#34;&gt;then, the cylinder&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I tried doing something with a few cylinders and some boolean operation. I also&#xA;applied a beveling to smooth the corners.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I added a space of half a millimeter between the lid and the box.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafybeigd4ihklxlf3pihd6ro647qx2s3cq7lvknboqwq5gwvmnkuceyzti?filename=bottle_box.blend&#34;&gt;bottle_box.blend&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;/blog/ipfs/bafybeickotxpnjv4qye2fbkk5e7q4edk563tpxjca7svcxgj2nbom4c7oa/stl_viewer.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;stl_cont&#34; id=&#34;stl_cont_5fbbecf6289f5fd1d1590c21f84f068c&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;script&gt;var stl_viewer=new StlViewer(document.getElementById(&#34;stl_cont_5fbbecf6289f5fd1d1590c21f84f068c&#34;), { models: [ {id:0, filename:&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafkreihbcctc522mbrjqeax756pn6mv4il2ft3so3k7monkginhwte3asa?filename=lid.stl&#34;} ] });&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;(&lt;a href=&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafkreihbcctc522mbrjqeax756pn6mv4il2ft3so3k7monkginhwte3asa?filename=lid.stl&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-download&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;/blog/ipfs/bafybeickotxpnjv4qye2fbkk5e7q4edk563tpxjca7svcxgj2nbom4c7oa/stl_viewer.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;stl_cont&#34; id=&#34;stl_cont_7622e7a868a45e2adca1a1c02306f2fc&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;script&gt;var stl_viewer=new StlViewer(document.getElementById(&#34;stl_cont_7622e7a868a45e2adca1a1c02306f2fc&#34;), { models: [ {id:0, filename:&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafkreigupm3htiihmm6peprdfxglo5y3lnhd27njdusml427yp3bbc2rmm?filename=box.stl&#34;} ] });&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;(&lt;a href=&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafkreigupm3htiihmm6peprdfxglo5y3lnhd27njdusml427yp3bbc2rmm?filename=box.stl&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-download&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It looks quite good. I think the space could be a little smaller for the lid to&#xA;better hold.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafybeicqe2huhkuy5arkmdrqhswgfmozgef6wedwmmzn2usfq7zehtrf7i?filename=a.png&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;making-the-lid-a-little-bit-bigger&#34;&gt;making the lid a little bit bigger&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://konubinix.eu/ipfs/bafybeifwguq6gm6vju5xxc5czagsc3337j4g3ssnnsq22xktjofpe6rafu?filename=bottle_box.blend&#34;&gt;bottle_box.blend&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Now it quite ok.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
